  "baseRefName": "main",
  "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds the **V10 institutional scale layer** for Dealix, extending the repo into a complete operating company system for scale, board governance, enterprise sales, profitability, localization, productization, operating leverage, moat metrics, executive demo days, and CEO cockpit.\n\n> Note: developed on the session-designated branch `claude/dealix-v10-institutional-scale-dVZTW` (per environment branch policy) rather than `final/dealix-institutional-scale-market-domination-v10`.\n\n## Includes\n\n18 operating systems (each with docs + a `99_*_REPORT.md`):\n\n* Institutional Scale OS\n* Board Governance OS\n* Market Domination OS\n* Enterprise Sales Room OS\n* Customer Advisory OS\n* Commercial Legal Readiness OS\n* Profitability OS\n* Scope Control OS\n* Case Study Governance OS\n* Competitive Win Room OS\n* Saudi/GCC Localization OS\n* Talent Bench OS\n* Productization OS\n* Operating Leverage OS\n* Safe Lifecycle Automation OS\n* Moat Metrics OS\n* Executive Demo Day OS\n* CEO Cockpit OS\n\nPlus:\n\n* **Generators** (write drafts/reports under `outputs/`): `ceo_cockpit_generate.py`, `board_packet_generate.py`, `enterprise_sales_room_generate.py`, `executive_demo_day_pack_generate.py`, `profitability_summary.py`, `moat_metrics_summary.py`\n* **Verification**: 11 per-OS verifiers + 5 aggregators (`company_utilization_verify`, `startup_os_verify`, `final_launch_control_verify`, `master_startup_command_verify`, `execution_intelligence_verify`) + `v10_master_verification.py`\n* **Tests**: 14 V10 test files (34 tests)\n* **GitHub Actions**: `v10-master-verification.yml`, `v10-institutional-scale.yml`, `v10-ceo-cockpit.yml` — all `workflow_dispatch` + `schedule`, `permissions: contents: read`, artifact-only, no secrets, no external sending, no commits\n* **Config/data**: `config/profitability_model_schema.json` + example JSONL inputs (synthetic assumptions only)\n* Reports + Master Verification under `outputs/v10_verification/`\n\n`238 files changed, +10,012` (145 docs, 26 scripts, 14 tests, 3 workflows).\n\n## Safety\n\nThe unbreakable rule is embedded in every document and enforced by tests/verifiers:\n\n> AI prepares, analyzes, drafts, scores, ranks, and recommends. Founder reviews, approves, signs, sells, sends manually, and decides. **The system never sends externally.**\n\n* No external sending (Email / WhatsApp / LinkedIn)\n* No SMTP, no secrets, no API keys\n* No scraping, no auto-submit, no LinkedIn automation\n* No live paid ads, no fake traction, no guaranteed ROI\n* No unverified security/compliance claims (a negation-aware scanner blocks affirmative \"guaranteed ROI\" / fake-cert claims; prohibitive policy text passes)\n* No external sending from GitHub Actions; founder approval remains required\n\n## Tests Run (real results)\n\n* `python scripts/v10_master_verification.py` → **V10_MASTER_VERIFICATION=PASS** (all 11 OS PASS)\n* 5 aggregators → all **PASS**\n* `pytest` (14 V10 test files, `--noconftest`) → **34 passed**\n* `ruff check` (V10 files) → **All checks passed**\n* `black --check --target-version py311` (V10 files) → **clean**\n* `make env-check` → **PASS**\n* `make security-smoke` → fails only on **pre-existing** placeholder-secret matches (no V10 file flagged)\n* `make api-contract-check` / `make test` → require the full app dependency set (fastapi/httpx) which is not installed in this ephemeral environment; the standalone V10 suite passes in isolation\n\n## Final Go/No-Go\n\n**GO:** CEO cockpit generation · board packet generation · enterprise sales room preparation · profitability review · localization review · productization planning · moat metrics · executive demo day packs · operating leverage planning\n\n**NO-GO:** external sending · platform automation · fake traction · live paid ads · unreviewed legal claims · fake security/compliance claims\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01DoPswTJWqLsz2zDLXAx3wm\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01DoPswTJWqLsz2zDLXAx3wm)_",
